<font face="verdana,arial" size=3>
<b>The following are new in the 2nd Generation beta <font color="red">2.0.0</font> version:
</b> 
</font>
<hr>
<font  face="verdana,arial" size=2>

<b>NOTE:</b>
<ul>
<P>
 This release is not officially recommended to update the existing Deployment 1.1 !<p>
 Inofficially, you can do an update under certain conditions <a href="update_d11_b200_conditions.htm">described in this document</a>. 
<br>
If you are unsure and want to be on the safe side, please wait for the release version
that is intended to update the Deployment 1.1.
</ul>
<p>
<b>A. PostgreSQL support</b>
 <blockquote>
<li>PostgreSQL database is now supported in addition to the mySQL.
<li>Test runs were done with PostgreSQL 7.2
<li>The auto-installer can install either in mySQL or PostgreSQL
</blockquote>
<p>
<b>B. Patches</b>
 <blockquote>
<li>The recent <a href="whats_new_1_1_0_1.htm" target=_blank>Patch D-1.1.0.1</a> was also incorporated in this release.
<li>New patches specific to display of TTF fonts in  Arabic language  (Walid Fathalla)
</blockquote>
<p>
<b>C. New Features and Improvements</b>
 <blockquote>
<li>Smarty 2.6.0 Template System (added by T. Wiedmann)
<li>Improved configurator for departments (Kurt Brauchli)
<li>Improved immunization module and automatic zip code input (Jean-Philippe LIOT)
<li>Added button on the admission data page to go directly to registration data page
</blockquote>
<p>
<b> D. CDS - Central Data Server and HXP Server</b>
 <blockquote>
This version has an experimental support for Central Data Server using the HXP exchange protocol. For details please <a href="howto_cds_hxp.htm">go here</a>.
</blockquote>
<p>
<b> E. Language and Help files</b>
 <blockquote>

 <li> Chinese-simplified
<li> German
<li> Spanish
</blockquote>

<p>
<b>F.  Coding System</b>
 <blockquote>
<li> Spanish ICD10 and OPS301 (Dr. Montemayor)
</blockquote>

